INSERT INTO github_project_links (id, project_id, github_project_id, github_owner, github_repo, github_project_number)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            RETURNING
                id as "id!: Uuid",
                project_id as "project_id!: Uuid",
                github_project_id,
                github_owner,
                github_repo,
                github_project_number as "github_project_number: i64",
                sync_enabled as "sync_enabled!: bool",
                last_sync_at as "last_sync_at: DateTime<Utc>",
                created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
